Class Packet

  • java.lang.Object
    • eu.cifpfbmoll.netlib.packet.Packet

  • public class Packet
extends Object
    Defines the structure of a packet to be sent to other nodes on the network.

    Instances of this Class must be created using the Constructor Factory Method

      • create

        public static Packet create(String type,
                            Integer src,
                            Integer dst,
                            byte[] data)
        Create a new Packet without specifying the Time to Live field and the resend ID.

        Time to Live will have its default value. The resend ID will be the same as the source ID.

        Parameters:
        type - packet type
        src - source node id
        dst - destination node id
        data - packet data
        Returns:
        new Packet instance
